r_Things_Matthew_Modine.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Stranger_Things_Matthew_Modine-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Stranger_Things_Matthew_Modine-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Stranger_Things_Matthew_Modine-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Stranger_Things_Matthew_Modine-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Stranger_Things_Matthew_Modine-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-2771448" class="wp-caption-text">马修·莫迪恩在《怪奇物语》中饰演布伦纳博士，米莉·鲍比·布朗饰演十一号。图片来源：Netflix</figcaption></figure><p>今年二月，布朗在<em>《吉米·法伦今夜秀》</em>节目中<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/stranger-things-fans-bewildered-over-millie-bobby-browns-new-accent-in-interview-3596480">首次分享了她与邦吉奥维订婚的故事</a>，并表示她之前没有谈论过这件事，因为她想将“关键时刻”保密。</p><p>然而，她告诉法伦，邦乔维的求婚故事“太好了，无法不说”，因为他是在水下实现的。</p><p> “他把戒指戴在我手上，当我向他展示时，戒指从我的手指上掉了下来，坠落得如此之快，”这位女演员回忆道。 “杰克跳进水里，好深。就像，潜水员[教练]说，‘你不能这样做。你的耳朵——毫不夸张地说，你的大脑会爆炸。”</p><p>她补充道：“我真的觉得这反映了他是谁，我觉得我们永远都会互相支持。如果有人掉球，我们就得到了。” </p><figure id="attachment_3501113" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3501113" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3501113" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Millie-Bobby-Brown-jake-bongiovi@2000x1270.jpg" alt="杰克·邦焦维和米莉·鲍比·布朗" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Millie-Bobby-Brown-jake-bongiovi@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Millie-Bobby-Brown-jake-bongiovi@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Millie-Bobby-Brown-jake-bongiovi@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Millie-Bobby-Brown-jake-bongiovi@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/Millie-Bobby-Brown-jake-bongiovi@2000x1